WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.160
When I tell people

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:06.936
that I'm trying to develop
a contraceptive pill for men,

00:00:06.960 --> 00:00:10.680
the response usually varies
along gender lines.

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.976
Women say something like,

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.296
"Fantastic. It's about time. When?"

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:17.616
(Laughter)

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:19.736
Men have one of two responses.

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.976
They either love the idea,

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:24.056
or they look at me a little warily

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:27.576
and wonder what exactly
I have in store for their testicles.

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:30.336
(Laughter)